<item>
            <title>[LU-14123] WBC: better DNE support</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-14123</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In the current design:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;All files under a root WBC directory are allocated with FIDs located on the&#160;same target (MDT).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;And also in current implementation, it does not support default LMV on the root WBC directory.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The above design can simply the batched metadata update and recovery (no any dependency)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;TODO: &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;In the future, files under a root WBC directory could be distributed across&#160;MDT targets other than the one which the root WBC directory located&#160;on. This could increase concurrency for metadata performance.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
